OL,3,CMan could survive to stand trial over
OL,4,Cmurder of mum and children
OL,6,FA murder suspect who has been in a
OL,7,Fcoma since a house fire that killed a
OL,8,Fmother and her three children may now
OL,9,Frecover sufficiently to stand trial, a
OL,10,Fcourt has heard.
OL,12,FBryonie Gawith, 29, died following the
OL,13,Fblaze at her home in Westbury Road,
OL,14,FBradford, in the early hours of 21
OL,15,FAugust last year.
OL,17,FHer children Denisty Birtle, nine,
OL,18,FOscar Birtle, five, and 22-month-old
OL,19,FAubree Birtle also suffered fatal
OL,20,Finjuries.
