OL,3,CMan could survive to stand trial over
OL,4,Cmurder of mum and children
OL,6,FThe man was arrested at the scene.
OL,8,FBradford Crown Court previously heard
OL,9,Fhe was in a coma and would not be
OL,10,Fready for trial "even if he does wake
OL,11,Fup".
OL,13,FOn Monday, prosecutor Matthew Bean
OL,14,Fsaid it had been thought the man "was
OL,15,Fnot expected to survive, or if he did,
OL,16,Fit was going to take a considerable
OL,17,Famount of time for him to recover".
