OL,3,CMan could survive to stand trial over
OL,4,Cmurder of mum and children
OL,6,FBut he told the hearing: "In January
OL,7,Fand February, we received updates
OL,8,Findicating a marked improvement in his
OL,9,Fcondition.
OL,11,F"The summary of the current prognosis
OL,12,F... (he) is expected to survive and
OL,13,Fthe expected timescale for discharge
OL,14,Ffrom hospital is between a number of
OL,15,Fweeks to a small number of months."
OL,17,FThe court heard he may be fit to stand
OL,18,Ftrial by the end of the year.
