OL,3,CMan could survive to stand trial over
OL,4,Cmurder of mum and children
OL,6,FTwo other men - Mohammed Shabir, 44,
OL,7,Fof Alice Street, Keighley, and Calum
OL,8,FSunderland, 25, of Calton Street,
OL,9,FKeighley - are due to go on trial next
OL,10,Fweek after pleading not guilty to
OL,11,Fmurdering Ms Gawith and the three
OL,12,Fchildren, and attempting to murder Ms
OL,13,FGawith's sister, Antonia Gawith.
OL,15,FAn application to delay the trial so
OL,16,Fthe three men can stand trial together
OL,17,Fif the third suspect is charged was
OL,18,Fadjourned until next week.
